<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَلَقَدْ يَسَّرْنَا القُرْآنَ لِلذِّكْرِ , فَهَلْ مِنْ مُدَّكِرٍ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص١٥٩:</span> يُقَالُ: مُيَسَّرٌ: مُهَيَّأٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> يَسَّرْنَا القُرْآنَ بِلِسَانِكَ: هَوَّنَّا قِرَاءَتَهُ عَلَيْكَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مَطَرٌ الوَرَّاقُ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَلَقَدْ يَسَّرْنَا القُرْآنَ لِلذِّكْرِ فَهَلْ مِنْ مُدَّكِرٍ}</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> هَلْ مِنْ طَالِبِ عِلْمٍ فَيُعَانَ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [القمر: ١٧]</p> </div>